        <h1 style="font-size: 2rem;">Guidelines for Adding Sections and Quizzes</h1>
        <br />
                

        <p>Welcome to the guidelines page for adding new sections and quizzes.</p>


        <h2>How to Add a New Section</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Navigate to the "Create Section" page.</li>
            <li>Fill in the section name and description.</li>
            <li>Click the "Save" button to create the section.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>How to Add a New Quiz</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Navigate to the section where you want to add the quiz.</li>
            <li>Click the "Quiz" button.</li>
            <li>Fill in the quiz details such as name, description.</li>
            <li>Click on "Save" button to create the quiz.</li>
            <li>Add questions to the quiz by clicking the "Add Question" button.</li>
            <li>Fill in the text for the question and the points that correspond to it, and click on "Save" button to add the question.</li>
            <li>Then for each question, click on "Add answer" and fill in the information for the answers provided. </li>
            <li>Click the "Save" button to create the quiz.</li>
        </ol>

        <h6>Note: You have to create a final section for the course, in order for final quiz to be automatically generated!</h6>
        <h6>Follow the guidelines:</h6>
        <h2>How to Add the Final section as a summary of the course</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Navigate to the "Create Section" page.</li>
            <li>Fill in the section name with value "Final" and the description.</li>
            <li>Click the "Save" button to create the section.</li>
        </ol>


        <h2>How final quiz is generated?</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Head to the functionalities provided for the "Final" section.</li>
            <li>Click on button "Quiz" to provide the name of the final quiz.</li>
            <li>Set the value of Quiz name to "Final".</li>
            <li>Click the "Save" button to automatically generate the final quiz.</li>
            <li>The final quiz is set to be automatically created when "Save" button is created.</li>
            <li>Final quiz will consist of all questions of all the quizzes of all Sections of the Course.</li>

        </ol>

        <p>If you have any questions, please contact the system administrator for assistance.</p>
